:

1. *Žive* deca su se igrala na ulici. (The living children were playing in the street.)
2. *Živi* večno u srcima našim. (It lives forever in our hearts.)
3. *Živela* je u staroj kući. (She lived in an old house.)
4. *Živeo* je više od sedamdeset godina. (He lived more than seventy years.)
5. *Živi* još uvek njihova priča. (Their story still lives.)